About Us

After years of moving from warehouse to warehouse, we grew tired of never finding a place that accommodated the needs of its renters. So in 2005, Featherstone Business Park was established with the goal of addressing this concern. Since then, we have been serving businesses like yours with commercial warehouse spaces for nearly 20 years, and we take pride in knowing that we have successfully achieved our initial goal. Featherstone Business Park embraces a helpful and friendly culture where businesses can thrive, and we would love to have you apart of our community.

About Us

After years of moving from warehouse to warehouse, we grew tired of never finding a place that accommodated the needs of its renters. So in 2005, Featherstone Business Park was established with the goal of addressing this concern. Since then, we have been serving businesses like yours with commercial warehouse spaces for nearly 20 years, and we take pride in knowing that we have successfully achieved our initial goal. Featherstone Business Park embraces a helpful and friendly culture where businesses can thrive, and we would love to have you apart of our community.

Hassle-Free Renting

Featherstone Business Park has been and will be locally owned and operated. This means no dealing with larger companies who make it difficult to get a problem fixed or simply pay rent. The warehouse owner has his own unit at the front of the property and is there on most days, making communication as easy as just stopping by. As a result of this, issues can be resolved extremely quickly, giving you more time to focus on your business. Additionally, there are no contractual gimmicks or fine-prints. Simply make an initial deposit and pay every month via PayPal, Zelle, Check, Money Order, or Direct Deposit.

24/7 Gate-code Access

The gate is open on weekdays from 7am to 6pm, but can be opened at any time with a personal gate code. This affords you the convenience and flexibility of accessing the property whenever you need, while still ensuring your goods and belongings remain safe and secure.

24/7 Surveillance

Security cameras provide extensive coverage and comprehensive views of the entire property, giving you peace of mind and confidence in the safety of your valuable assets.

Location

We are located right off of N Saginaw Blvd (Business 287) and just 2 miles from U.S. Highway 287, making our location perfect for ease of access and convenience. Additionally, with the rapid growth of the Alliance Corridor and surrounding areas, we are in the perfect location to help you grow your business in the North Fort Worth area.
